00:48:06.957 --> 00:48:08.540
JOYCE CHITTICK: Need
to be maintained.

00:48:08.540 --> 00:48:11.510
MELISSA BENOIST: And need to
be maintained and taken care of

00:48:11.510 --> 00:48:13.150
and used properly and healthily.

